des: Want to lead a simpler, calmer life in just 30 days? Launch this skill every day for 30 days to get a new small step you can take to minimize the clutter, noise, and negative influences in your life. At the end of 30 days, you'll be amazed at how different your mindset is. Take one small step each day to change your life forever.
